					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Actually, the proper way to hide unused sprites is to set their Y-coordinate to any value between $F0 and $FF (inclusive), thereby placing it off the bottom of the screen.
<br />
<br />(edit: F0-F7 is also valid; technically, EF is too)</div>

					
