						<div class="postbody">Well, if you are testing on the real NES, you won't be able to see sprites in the corner, will you? Actually, at least not the whole thing, the bottom 8 pixels, correct? I would just stick with not using tile #0. If you want to use it for sprite #0 hits, just put a line of pixels on the top of the tile, so you won't be able to see it on the real system, but it still is usable for doing that.</div>

